<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1912-09-11T14:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1912-09-11T14:00:00-05:00" n="1160" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1160">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/4880.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Consul at
                                    Nogales</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                    State</gloss></hi>.</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Extract.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Naco, Ariz.</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-09-11T12:00:00-07:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">September 11, 1912—12
                                noon</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Rojas, Mascarenas, and Rafael Campa with about 600 men are about 10 miles
                            south of Aguaprieta and have demanded its surrender, saying they would
                            attack in the morning.</p>
                        <p>Entire shipment of arms and ammunition sent in my care has now reached
                            here, and I have placed it temporarily in Chargé of commanding officer
                            United States troops, who, for greater safety, has placed entire
                            shipment under military guard at Bisbee, 8 miles from the boundary.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Dye.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>